# ERROR TIPS
### Errors when using burner equipment without fuel
- Ensure that the burner equipment has fuel before attempting to use it.
### Errors when using inserter without source items
- Ensure that the inserter has source items before attempting to use it.
### Errors when using furnace without ingredients
- Ensure that the furnace has ingredients before attempting to use it.
### Errors when using steam engine without connection
- Ensure that the steam engine is connected to a boiler and a power source before attempting to use it.
### Errors when using electricity group without being plugged into electric network
- Ensure that the electricity group is plugged into an electric network before attempting to use it.
